'''顾纪筠'''（{{lang-en|Priscilla Koo Kei Kwan}}，{{bd|1962年|9月1日<ref>{{cite news |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20120903/18006318 |title=顧紀筠生日玩懷舊 |newspaper=蘋果日報 |date=2012-09-03 |accessdate=2017-04-11 |archive-date=2017-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412063029/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20120903/18006318 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180906/bkn-20180906100348625-0906_00862_001.html |title=鄭裕玲顧紀筠生日　閨蜜蒲頭合體慶祝 |date=2018-09-06 |work=東網 |accessdate=2018-09-12 |language=zh-yue |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023115111/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180906/bkn-20180906100348625-0906_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/232369/%E9%84%AD%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B261%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E6%90%9E%E9%96%A8%E8%9C%9C%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E8%87%B3%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%83-%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E5%AD%96%E5%AE%A3%E8%90%B1%E4%B8%98%E5%87%B1%E6%95%8F%E9%BD%8A%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB |title=鄭裕玲61歲生日搞閨蜜派對 「至八會」顧紀筠孖宣萱丘凱敏齊現身 |date=2018-09-06 |work=香港01 |accessdate=2018-09-12 |language=zh-yue |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026034715/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/232369/%E9%84%AD%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B261%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E6%90%9E%E9%96%A8%E8%9C%9C%E6%B4%BE%E5%B0%8D-%E8%87%B3%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%83-%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E5%AD%96%E5%AE%A3%E8%90%B1%E4%B8%98%E5%87%B1%E6%95%8F%E9%BD%8A%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB |dead-url=no }}</ref>|||K顧}}），籍貫[[中国|中国]][[上海|上海]]，綽號「'''顧老闆'''」，[[香港|香港]][[主持人|主持人]]，曾任[[香港足球總會|香港足球總會]]市務及傳訊委員會成員。其「'''顧老闆'''」的綽號來自藝人同事給她的稱呼<ref name="放學後 第五集" />。

==背景==
顧紀筠早年居於[[香港島|香港島]][[麥當勞道|麥當勞道]]<ref name="Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計">{{cite web |url=https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/culture/daily/article/20140320/18661913 |title=Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計 |last= |first= |date=2014-03-20|website= |publisher=香港蘋果日報 |access-date=2020-02-09|quote=}}</ref>，家有一名較她小八歲的胞弟<ref name="【放學後】顧紀筠發奮脫貧廿多歲半山置業 顧老闆：訂下目標否則人生只有享樂">{{cite news | title=【放學後】顧紀筠發奮脫貧廿多歲半山置業 顧老闆：訂下目標否則人生只有享樂 | url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2466624/%E3%80%90%E6%94%BE%E5%AD%B8%E5%BE%8C%E3%80%91%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E7%99%BC%E5%A5%AE%E8%84%AB%E8%B2%A7%E5%BB%BF%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%80%E9%A1%A7%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%EF%BC%9A%E8%A8%82%E4%B8%8B%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%AB%E6%A8%82 | format= | publisher=經濟日報 | date=2019-10-07 | accessdate=2020-02-10 | quote= | archive-date=2020-08-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818091401/https://topick.hket.com/article/2466624/%E3%80%90%E6%94%BE%E5%AD%B8%E5%BE%8C%E3%80%91%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E7%99%BC%E5%A5%AE%E8%84%AB%E8%B2%A7%E5%BB%BF%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E3%80%80%E9%A1%A7%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%EF%BC%9A%E8%A8%82%E4%B8%8B%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%AB%E6%A8%82 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。11歲時因做鞋廠生意的父親生意失敗和投資失利而遷居[[香港仔|香港仔]][[田灣邨|田灣邨]]{{noteTag|資料出自無綫電視於2017年4月2日播出的綜藝節目《屋邨遊樂團》第4集。}}，曾在該屋邨的一所[[天台小學|天台小學]]讀書<ref>{{cite news | title=教育節目製作逾年 碌盡人情卡 | url=http://www.takungpao.com.hk/231106/2019/0918/349959.html | format= | publisher=大公報 | date=2019-09-18 | accessdate=2020-02-09 | quote= | archive-date=2020-08-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818091419/http://www.takungpao.com.hk/231106/2019/0918/349959.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計" />。她的父親之後轉到顧紀筠姑丈的[[黃竹坑|黃竹坑]]廠房當廠長<ref name="放學後 第五集" />，母親則於[[澳洲|澳洲]]工作<ref name="放學後 第五集" />。其名字「紀筠」為「紀溫」的諧音，因為她出生時正值[[颱風溫黛_(1962年)|颱風溫黛]]吹襲香港，家人藉此來紀念「溫黛」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191004/1570180651431/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%82%E6%9B%BE%E4%BD%8F%E5%BE%99%E7%BD%AE%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E7%99%BC%E5%A5%AE-%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E5%8D%80%E8%B2%B7%E5%B1%8B%E8%B4%88%E9%9B%99%E8%A6%AA |title=【童年時曾住徙置區】顧紀筠發奮 半山區買屋贈雙親 |last= |first= |date=2019-10-04 |website= |publisher=明報 |access-date=2020-02-09 |quote= |archive-date=2020-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818091454/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191004/1570180651431/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E6%99%82%E6%9B%BE%E4%BD%8F%E5%BE%99%E7%BD%AE%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E7%99%BC%E5%A5%AE-%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E5%8D%80%E8%B2%B7%E5%B1%8B%E8%B4%88%E9%9B%99%E8%A6%AA |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她就讀中學期間曾演唱民歌<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠謙虛密實原來彈得又唱得 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFEtw1F74677i&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=5  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1981-09-19| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>。在17歲那年中五畢業後<ref name="安哥同學會 - 顧紀筠訪問" />，先在[[胡楓|胡楓]]位於[[旺角|旺角]]的影片發行公司任職文員<ref name="放學後 第五集" />，再到珠寶批發行任職銷售員<ref name="Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計" />，為時一年。

1980年，顧紀筠加入[[麗的電視|麗的電視]]<ref>{{cite news | title=性格不適應這圈子 顧紀筠爲前途躊躇 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFDgpMLpsneyZ&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=20&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1982-04-25| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>，主要任主持。其餘時間花在於大一藝術設計學院進修三年制珠寶櫥窗設計課程<ref name="Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計" /><ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠要學商科 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv595P2B4OmBy5yxAurl2RUGS&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=26&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=26  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1981-03-25| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>。亦修讀過[[澳門大學|澳門大學]]工商管理課程<ref name="放學後 第五集" />。又會打理自己的廣告製作與珠寶訂製公司業務<ref name="放學後 第五集" /><ref>{{cite news | title=螢影星聲 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv595P2B4OmBy5xPc%2FRBVyedv&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=25&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=30  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1982-04-15| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠精打細算是個出色生意人 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFGWJs%2BjDRMLy&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=9&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=4  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1982-05-12| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>。往後在美國修讀為期半年的珠寶鑑證課程<ref name="Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計" />。顧之所以在幕前發展源於她於1980年4月參加麗的電視為期三個月的「慧眼識新星」藝員訓練班時<ref name="安哥同學會 - 顧紀筠訪問" />，由於表現出色，結果在同年7月的簽約儀式中與李秉鏜、[[莫少聰|莫少聰]]、[[倪詩蓓|倪詩蓓]]、方珍妮等學員一同被簽為麗的旗下藝人<ref>{{cite news | title=「慧眼識新星」盛會 五位新星簽約加盟 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFBxpgTwoUGnC&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=11&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=3 | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1980-07-11 | accessdate=2020-02-09 | quote= | archive-date=2020-07-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717023114/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFBxpgTwoUGnC&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=11&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她一直留在[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]至1990年代末轉投[[無綫電視|無綫電視]]。此前於亞洲電視主持節目之外，也曾演出少量亞視和[[香港電台|香港電台]]劇集。其首部參演的電視劇是《[[驟雨中的陽光續集|驟雨中的陽光續集]]》<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠演驟雨陽光 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFFzFRyHymOoC&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=5  | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1980-11-03| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>。當時[[黎小田|黎小田]]認為顧的歌喉不錯，於是向電視台高層推薦她與[[林國雄_(演員)|林國雄]]合唱《驟雨中的陽光續集》插曲；然而最終未能成事<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠頻練歌準備唱主題曲 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFCLLem%2B5QAhO&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=7&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=6 | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1980-11-13 | accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>。

及後，顧紀筠在1983年轉簽節目部頭主持合約<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠調主持 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58StS6UNkXpimngvLV0lpVo&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=4&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=9  | publisher=香港工商日報 | date=1983-05-09| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠約滿亞視 以部頭主持「勁運縱橫」 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58Sngm8Qm6Mn9t61C6w9xvd&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=30&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=22  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1983-03-12| accessdate=2020-02-09|quote= }}</ref>，以主持體育節目為主。1987年在[[香港理工學院|香港理工學院]]進修勞工法例相關課程<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠有一六月大兒子 望多追一個女兒 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5EnoToocCUWPS&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=45&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=14  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1987-03-12| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>。至1988年，顧紀筠移民[[加拿大|加拿大]]<ref>{{cite news | title=自謂控制丈夫有妙法 顧紀筠留兒在身邊 乖乖的自坐移民監 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJCUeV%2FM9XAFC&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=41&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=24  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1988-11-13 | accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>，1989年一度居於當地，且入職加拿大中文電視台<ref>{{cite news | title=為遷就主持奧運節目 加國電視台工作 顧紀筠延遲上任 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJN4asHDnl8Ve&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=55&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=15  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1988-05-10| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>。但礙於該處工資太低，因此與兒子一同回港生活<ref>{{cite news | title=Do姐飯局56歲顧紀筠凍齡好省鏡 樂做滿分繼母超錫阿仔陳浚霆 | url=https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2440652/Do%E5%A7%90%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%8056%E6%AD%B2%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E5%87%8D%E9%BD%A1%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%81%E9%8F%A1%20%E6%A8%82%E5%81%9A%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%86%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E8%B6%85%E9%8C%AB%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%94%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%9A%E9%9C%86 | format= | publisher=晴報 | date=2019-08-30 | accessdate=2020-02-10 | quote= | archive-date=2020-08-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818091535/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2440652/Do%E5%A7%90%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%8056%E6%AD%B2%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E5%87%8D%E9%BD%A1%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%81%E9%8F%A1%20%E6%A8%82%E5%81%9A%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%86%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E8%B6%85%E9%8C%AB%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%94%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%9A%E9%9C%86 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。1990年重返亞洲電視，而且簽了兩年主持兼演員合約，主力主持與世界盃及其他體育賽事有關的節目<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠重返亞視 兒子將交前夫養 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJK94NOKChjgv&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=71&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=23  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1990-01-24| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>。而於無綫電視工作後，開始為人所熟悉，多於大型節目中與[[曾志偉|曾志偉]]等拍檔擔任主持工作。在2003年再婚後，顧淡出娛樂圈，並在珠寶業發展<ref name="Big Spender：顧紀筠 沉醉珠寶設計" />。於珠寶界發展的原因出於自小受喜歡戴首飾姑媽耳濡目染<ref>{{cite news | title=【揚眉女子】顧紀筠曾住徙置區發憤脫貧 廿多歲半山置業兌現中學許下承諾 | url=https://topick.hket.com/article/2777740/%E3%80%90%E6%8F%9A%E7%9C%89%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E3%80%91%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E6%9B%BE%E4%BD%8F%E5%BE%99%E7%BD%AE%E5%8D%80%E7%99%BC%E6%86%A4%E8%84%AB%E8%B2%A7%E3%80%80%E5%BB%BF%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%8C%E7%8F%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%A8%B1%E4%B8%8B%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE | page= | publisher=香港經濟日報 | date=2020-10-15 | accessdate=2021-04-15 | quote= | archive-date=2021-01-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128000651/https://topick.hket.com/article/2777740/%E3%80%90%E6%8F%9A%E7%9C%89%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E3%80%91%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E6%9B%BE%E4%BD%8F%E5%BE%99%E7%BD%AE%E5%8D%80%E7%99%BC%E6%86%A4%E8%84%AB%E8%B2%A7%E3%80%80%E5%BB%BF%E5%A4%9A%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%8C%E7%8F%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%A8%B1%E4%B8%8B%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她曾在2001年出版[[散文|散文]]集《給親愛的 關於成長的70封信》。另外還有九本著作。2020年復出為互聯網媒體平台NEW TV主持節目《顧老闆‧請客》<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠復出主持節目 探討香港熱話 | url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20200819/s00016/1597775073210/%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%E5%BE%A9%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%8E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1 | page= | publisher=明報 | date=2020-08-19 | accessdate=2021-04-15 | quote= | archive-date=2020-08-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819042902/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%a8%9b%e6%a8%82/article/20200819/s00016/1597775073210/%e9%a1%a7%e7%b4%80%e7%ad%a0%e5%be%a9%e5%87%ba%e4%b8%bb%e6%8c%81%e7%af%80%e7%9b%ae-%e6%8e%a2%e8%a8%8e%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==其他資料==
顧紀筠在1989年創下藝人在電視史上演出580個節目的紀錄<ref>{{cite news | title=一年演五百八十個節目 顧紀筠破電視紀錄 簽新約減少工作量 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJDKYkNmbM4Ud&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=51&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=24  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1990-08-02| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref><ref name="安哥同學會 - 顧紀筠訪問" />。於1988年主持漢城奧運會節目期間，無綫電視總經理鄭君略曾代表無綫電視邀請她跳槽；最後顧因覺得做生不如做熟，便婉拒了鄭的好意<ref>{{cite news | title=做選美司儀要重新包裝 顧紀筠對挖角事願向鄭君略道歉 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJEWGPzsYvIs8&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=65&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=27  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1988-10-13 | accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>。2000年，中建電訊集團附屬機構CCT數碼資訊推出由顧紀筠親自主理的ecmind.com，內容主要圍繞在「顧紀筠自在天地」部分分享其內心世界和看法<ref>{{cite news | title=CCT數碼推出顧紀筠網頁 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/singpao/20000413/B14009.html | page= | publisher=成報 | date=2000-04-13 | accessdate=2021-04-15 | quote= | archive-date=2021-04-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415092922/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/singpao/20000413/B14009.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==家庭生活==
顧紀筠共有二段婚姻。她於1986年與龍厚殷成婚，於1986年產下一子。其丈夫從事資訊科技業<ref>{{cite news | title=丈夫在加坐移民監 顧紀筠甘做太空人 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJFfDVVA3V6lo&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=75&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=15  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1988-06-14| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>。卻在1989年因放不下香港的事業基礎，加上與在加拿大生活的丈夫長期分隔兩地而決定分居<ref name="不甘做太空人與夫辦離婚手續 顧紀筠謂已太成熟 大家思想距離很大" />，1997年才正式離婚<ref name="【放學後】顧紀筠發奮脫貧廿多歲半山置業 顧老闆：訂下目標否則人生只有享樂" />。她分居後未幾計劃於1992年與新任男友共諧連理<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠結婚要追個仔 陳法蓉妹入娛圈 月清辛苦有價值 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58JCjtBMMIqomgQa4kcOLRt&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=34&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=13  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1991-11-01| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref>。直至2003年，顧再度結婚，嫁給[[美國|美國]]思科系統全球高級副總裁兼大中華區董事長陳仕煒。婚後翌年全面投身商界至今。此外，她除了育有一名親生兒子、一名繼女和一名繼子[[陳浚霆|陳浚霆]]外，還透過[[保良局|保良局]]領養了兩名孤兒和助養了四名兒童<ref>{{cite news | title=顧紀筠再婚條件 要對方接受兒子 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJEplJWG75lpk&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=58&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%A1%A7%E7%B4%80%E7%AD%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | pages=18  | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1989-05-08| accessdate=2020-02-10|quote= }}</ref><ref name="助養兒童讓兒子知道自己幸福 兒子去加與父生活 顧紀筠不急於離婚" />。

